reviewText: My favorite Audie Murphy movie.  Unfortunately, it only came in Spanish.  I sent it back and tried ordering it again in English.  Them sent a replacement movie.  I gave up.
For those of you who have a multi-region player and like Audey Murphy westerns, or '50s westerns in general this is a treat. A fun movie with a horse who steals the show!
Any movie with Audie  Murphy is worth watching.
Another Audie Murphy classic well worth watching some very actors in this movie Would recommend. Owen 5/09/14

I chose this rating because I am an avid Audie Murphy fan and have been trying to get this movie for a long time.
The movie was as good as I remember it being when I first saw it many years ago.
Thank you Amazon for making it possible for me to see this great movie staring a great character once again.
Excellent movie, young cowboy on the run must depend on swaybacked horse called Tumbleweed. Hope you get it in USA format soon!
